{"tid":149817,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(小學常識科)有冇人覺得應該要將愛迪生除名,換上N. Tesla?","createTime":"2017-03-09T14:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T17:05:55.000Z","uid":78900,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7804da646991f93912e1799844ab901dbd4786d","tid":149817,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"個個小學應該都讀過愛迪生發明電燈呢段歷史, 但係好少人知道其實愛迪生同D 金融,石油大財團故意埋沒左N.Tesla發明由大氣中吸收電力??<br />\n愛迪生條仆街不斷搞小動作損害Tesla既名譽, 令人以為交流電係好危險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解宜家D教科書會用愛迪生條撚樣黎做例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尼古拉&middot;特斯拉（英語：Nikola Tesla，塞爾維亞語：Никола Тесла；1856年7月10日－1943年1月7日）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3p7u21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3p7u21.jpg&h=4ae0b24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塞爾維亞裔美籍發明家、物理學家、機械工程師、電機工程師和未來學家。他被認為是電力商業化的重要推動者，並因主要設計了現代交流電力系統而最為人知。在麥可&middot;法拉第發現的電磁場理論的基礎上，特斯拉在電磁場領域有著多項革命性的發明。他的多項相關的專利以及電磁學的理論研究工作是現代的無線通信和無線電的基石。<br />\n<br />\n在現代社會中處處可見特斯拉的遺產。撇開他在電磁學和工程上的成就，特斯拉也被認為對機器人、彈道學、資訊科學、核子物理學和理論物理學上等各種領域有貢獻[3][4]。許多他的成就已伴隨著一些爭議被應用，去支持著許多的非主流科學，如幽浮理論和新世紀神秘理論。特斯拉當代的欽佩者視他為「創造出二十世紀的人」[5]。國際單位制中的，用來衡量磁感應強度（也作磁通量密度）的單位，是以特斯拉的名字命名，符號T（由國際度量衡大會在1960年確立）。在塞爾維亞首都貝爾格勒有一座國際機場（即貝爾格勒尼古拉&middot;特斯拉機場）以他的名字命名。塞爾維亞紙幣上至今有他的頭像。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPrototype既發電器<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j77FEeA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj77FEeA.jpg&h=a442cc46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8feee0f47f00af039a48450b948f9ea7f873df9","tid":149817,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:04:45.000Z","msg":"影片 (中文): 科學&ldquo;超人&rdquo;尼古拉&middot;特斯拉 清晰完整版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=26wrAU_M9zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D26wrAU_M9zw&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAhxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=87408d2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=26wrAU_M9zw</a>"},{"pid":"df2e9a99db9b5ca86e5898bbb2189a45fc937620","tid":149817,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"佢既發明由無線電裝置, 交流電, 以至汽車引擎入面點火器既火星嘴都係由佢發明, 佢既功績絕對比得上愛迪生, 品德更加比愛迪生好100萬倍, Tesla係發明電力能源既時侯, 佢既宗旨就係希望不論窮富都可以享受電力帶來既好處, 令人類文明科技踏進一大步, 但係佢就因為咁高尚既理念俾當時既大財團抹殺晒 !!!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n點解D教科書要用愛迪生黎洗小學生個腦?!!!!!!還我Tesla !!!! </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fad827fcac663487a9e86032185b21f09f2e8917","tid":149817,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"DC &gt; AC"},{"pid":"eb34c71e6f4dbf7f9bdc8a935407de80870e9424","tid":149817,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DC &gt; AC</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm